android.car.diagnostic

类 FloatSensorIndex

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.diagnostic.FloatSensorIndex

  • public final class FloatSensorIndex
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a container for the indices of diagnostic sensors. The values are extracted by running packages/services/Car/tools/update-obd2-sensors.py against types.hal. DO NOT EDIT MANUALLY
